==English==
===Noun===
'''red pepper''' (''Plural:'' '''red peppers''')

#A red colored, [[ripe]], [[bell pepper|bell]] or [[sweet pepper]].  Unripe peppers of this variety are colored green and edible but not as sweet.
#{{US}}Spicy peppers.
#:''Crushed '''red pepper''' flakes add zest to pizza.''
